Class MssqlIncident

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aserg.model.Incident
      • org.aserg.model.MssqlIncident

  • public class MssqlIncident
extends Incident
    This class represents the Incident that where the attacker attempts to exploit the vulnerabilities emulated in the MSSQL service.
